------------------------------------
 Sunlight RubyMine IDE Color Scheme
------------------------------------

This color scheme is inspired from Xcode 4.


1) Copy the 'Sunlight.xml' file to your ~/Library/Preferences/RubyMine31/colors folder.

2) In RubyMine 3.1 (or higher) under Preferences > Editor > Colors & Fonts choose the
   Sunlight theme for your Scheme name.


That's it!


